name: MEISJE MET DE PAREL 04- JUNE.2021
description: A tribute to one of the paintings us Dutchies appreciate the most.  After the original by Golden Age painter Johannes Vermeer, shamelessly moshed up into a one-of-a-kind stunning high resolution piece of art. A combination of hand drawn work, based on Vermeer's masterpiece, combined with digitally reworked glitch art.    Press pause on any given frame to display any of the thousands of unique stills.    This particular piece is part of a series of 5 in 2021.  Every piece is signed by the artist.   For more info on artist LotteZ visit Twitter: @LotteZ13 of website www.lottez.com
